Privacy Policy
Last updated: Feb 14, 2025
Black Candy LLC (Black Candy) develops and publishes mobile games.
This Privacy Policy explains how and why we collect, use, and share certain data when you use our games.
Data We Collect
We may collect the following types of data automatically through the game:
Location Information - IP Address
Device identifiers - Advertising ID (Apple IDFA or Google Advertising ID)
Device Information - Device model, type of connection, OS, time zone
Usage Information - Information about how users interact with our games (for instance your game progress, in-app purchases and number of ads served)
Why We Collect Your Data
We collect your data for the following purposes:
Improve User Experience – Identify issues, optimize performance, and enhance gameplay.
Optimize Marketing & Advertising – Improve ad targeting and user acquisition campaigns.
Data Sharing
We do not sell the personal information of our users; however, we may share data with third-party companies that help us operate and improve our game (e.g., analytics and advertising).
